# FlatButton 扁平按钮

用于次要动作的轻量按钮样式。

## 基础用法
::TuffDemo{title="扁平按钮" description="基础、主色、小尺寸与加载状态。" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TuffFlatButton>默认</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton primary>主色</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton mini>小尺寸</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton loading>加载中</TuffFlatButton>
  </template>
---
#preview
<div class="tuff-demo-row">
  <tuff-flat-button>默认</tuff-flat-button>
